- How are you gonna do that?

488
00:44:57.870 --> 00:44:59.037
You're gonna do it.

489
00:44:59.246 --> 00:45:01.164
Go to the central console.
open up bolt of circuits.

490
00:45:01.331 --> 00:45:03.083
When I clear the roof
I'll let you know

491
00:45:03.291 --> 00:45:05.376
and you're gonna hit
the master bypass button.

492
00:45:05.627 --> 00:45:07.754
That's gonna fry
everything up here.

493
00:45:08.880 --> 00:45:10.590
Okay. I am going in now.

494
00:45:10.798 --> 00:45:14.510
Make sure you wait till I clear
the roof. I'll buy you some time.

495
00:45:23.476 --> 00:45:25.562
This looks important.

496
00:45:45.038 --> 00:45:47.957
I never had a taste
for this sort of thing.

497
00:45:48.166 --> 00:45:51.836
