deeply enjoying the suit.

498
00:46:00.010 --> 00:46:02.887
You finally outdid
yourself. Tony.

499
00:46:04.639 --> 00:46:07.266
It would've made
your father proud.

500
00:46:11.270 --> 00:46:13.939
It's ready. Tony!
Get off the roof!

501
00:46:32.289 --> 00:46:33.707
Tony!

502
00:46:34.792 --> 00:46:36.710
How ironic. Tony!

503
00:46:38.128 --> 00:46:40.547
Trying to free
the world of weapons.

504
00:46:40.755 --> 00:46:42.924
you gave it
the best one ever!

505
00:46:43.133 --> 00:46:45.218
