damage to the Arc reactor.

517
00:48:27.270 --> 00:48:29.480
"Iron Man". that's kinda catchy.
It's got a nice ring to it.

518
00:48:29.689 --> 00:48:32.608
It's not technically accurate.
since it's a gold-titanium alloy.

519
00:48:32.817 --> 00:48:35.319
but it's kinda attractive
name anyway.

520
00:48:35.527 --> 00:48:37.237
Here is your alibi.

521
00:48:38.196 --> 00:48:40.532
- Okay.
- You were on your yacht.

522
00:48:40.782 --> 00:48:42.951
We told Pepper to put
you in Avalon all night

523
00:48:43.118 --> 00:48:45.286
and sworn statements
from 50 of your guests.

524
00:48:45.495 --> 00:48:48.331
I was thinking maybe we should
say it was just Pepper and me.

525
00:48:48.539 --> 00:48:50.249
alone on the island.

526
00:48:51.208 --> 00:48:54.420
That's what happened.
Just read it word for word.

527
00:48:56.296 --> 00:48:58.215
There's nothing
about Stane here.

528
00:48:58.382 --> 00:49:01.092
That's been handled.
He's on vacation.

529
00:49:01.343 --> 00:49:04.262
Small aircraft have such
a poor safety record.

530
00:49:04.471 --> 00:49:07.056
What about this whole story
that it's a body guard?

531
00:49:07.265 --> 00:49:09.642
He's my body... ?
That's kinda flimsy.

532
00:49:09.809 --> 00:49:12.019
This isn't my first rodeo.
Mr. Stark.

533
00:49:12.228 --> 00:49:15.647
Just stick to the official statement
and soon this will all be behind you.

534
00:49:15.939 --> 00:49:18.191
You've got 90 seconds.

535
00:49:20.944 --> 00:49:22.654
Oh. agent Coulson.

536
00:49:23.071 --> 00:49:26.908
I just wanted to say thank you
very much for all of your help.

537
00:49:27.283 --> 00:49:30.328
That's what we do.
You'll be hearing from us.

538
00:49:30.536 --> 00:49:33.789
- From the Strategic Homeland...
- Just call us S.H.I.E.L.D.

539
00:49:33.956 --> 00:49:35.374
Right.

540
00:49:36.125 --> 00:49:39.127
- Lets get the show on the road.
- You know. it's actually...

541
00:49:39.336 --> 00:49:42.130
...not that bad... even I
don't think I'm Iron Man.

542
00:49:42.255 --> 00:49:44.049
- You're not Iron Man.
- Yeah I am.

543
00:49:44.215 --> 00:49:45.967
- You're not.
- Suite yourself.

544
00:49:46.259 --> 00:49:48.553
If I were Iron Man.
I'd have this girlfriend

545
00:49:48.719 --> 00:49:51.055
