clearly. With this...

575
00:51:27.643 --> 00:51:30.354
long list of character defects
and all the mistakes I've made.

576
00:51:30.521 --> 00:51:32.314
largely in public.

577
00:51:32.898 --> 00:51:35.401
- Just stick to the cards.
- Yeah. okay.

578
